public CamelEvent createExchangeFailureHandlingEvent(Exchange exchange, Processor failureHandler, boolean deadLetterChannel, String deadLetterUri) {     // unwrap delegate processor     Processor handler = failureHandler.     if (handler instanceof DelegateProcessor) {         handler = ((DelegateProcessor) handler).getProcessor().     }     return new ExchangeFailureHandlingEvent(exchange, handler, deadLetterChannel, deadLetterUri). }
